@startuml hand-off-session-flow

title hand_off_session mcp tool — baton 接力全链路 (plan-driven / generic 双模式 + adopt + task + cleanup)

actor Caller as C
participant "hand_off_session handler\n(hand-off-session.ts 1249 LOC)" as H
participant "handOffSessionImpl\n(hand-off-session-impl.ts 357 LOC)" as I
participant "spawn_session handler\n(spawn.ts)" as SP
participant "agentDeckTeamRepo" as TR
participant "taskRepo" as Tk
participant "runBatonCleanup\n(baton-cleanup.ts)" as BC
participant "sessionManager" as SM
participant "sessionRepo (DB)" as DB
participant "SDK adapter\n(claude-code / codex-cli)" as SDK
participant "fs" as Fs

== 入口:deny external + cwd 反查 (与 archive_plan 同款) ==

C -> H: invoke({plan_id?, prompt?, cwd?, adapter?, team_name?,\n  adopt_teammates?, archive_caller?, team_task_policy?, ...})
note right of H
  EXTERNAL_CALLER_ALLOWED.hand_off_session = false
  起 SDK session fork bomb 风险 (同 spawn_session / archive_plan)
end note

H -> DB: sessionRepo.get(callerSid) 反查 cwd
note right of DB
  REVIEW_56 §F9: fail-open 退化
  console.warn (与 archive-plan 对称)
  ok return 无 warnings 字段不 surface (设计取舍)
end note

== 双模式分流: plan-driven vs generic ==

alt plan_id 传 (plan-driven 模式)
  H -> I: handOffSessionImpl({planId, planFilePathOverride?, phaseLabel?})
  I -> Fs: resolve plan file path\n(fallback chain: .claude/plans/ → ref/plans/ → ~/.claude/plans/)
  I -> Fs: read plan frontmatter\n(parse YAML)
  I -> I: 校验 status == in_progress\n(不在 → reject)
  I -> I: 校验 worktree_path 字段非空
  I -> I: 构造 coldStartPrompt = "按 <plan-file-path> 接力\n(Phase: <phaseLabel>)?"
  I --> H: { planFilePath, worktreePath, mainRepo,\n  coldStartPrompt, isExternalWorktree }
  note right of I
    REVIEW_36 R2 HIGH-B + MED-C: external worktree
    (worktree 不在 mainRepo subtree) → handler 自动加
    mainRepo 进 spawn args.extra_allow_write (claude-code
    workspace-write 沙盒额外 writable roots)
  end note
else 无 plan_id (generic 模式 — CHANGELOG_99 新增)
  H -> H: 不调 impl,直接组装 generic 上下文\n(coldStartPrompt = args.prompt ?? "从上一个会话接力继续工作")
  note right of H
    cwd 默认 = caller cwd (与 plan-driven 默认 mainRepo 不同)
    适合: cwd 已失效 / 跨 repo 任务 / 任意 baton 接力场景
    phaseLabel / plan_file_path 字段 silently ignored
  end note
end

== Phase 1: spawn 新 SDK session (复用 spawn_session handler) ==

H -> H: cwd 兜底链\n(args.cwd > resolved.mainRepo > resolved.worktreePath / args.cwd > caller.cwd)
H -> H: cwdExists(cwd) precheck\n(CHANGELOG_99 R1 fix MED-4: 失效自动 fallback)

H -> SP: spawnSessionHandler({adapter, cwd, prompt: coldStartPrompt,\n  team_name?, permission_mode?, sandbox?, ..., handOffMode: true})
note right of SP
  handOffMode: true → spawn handler 完全跳过 spawn-guards
  三道防御 (depth check + fan-out + spawn-rate) + 永不写
  spawn-link (sessions.spawned_by / spawn_depth 保持 null/0)
  hand-off 是平级接力非派遣关系
end note

SP -> SDK: createSession(opts) → 子进程起 SDK
SDK --> SP: realSessionId
SP -> DB: sessionRepo.upsert(newSid, ...)
SP --> H: { sessionId: newSid, teamId?, teamName?, spawnPromptMessageId? }

== Phase 1.5: adopt_teammates 路径 (plan hand-off-session-adopt-teammates-20260520) ==

alt adopt_teammates == true
  H -> H: N5 ≥1 lead 硬约束: caller 必须至少在 1 个 team 是 lead
  alt caller 不在任一 team 是 lead
    H -> SM: closeSession(newSid) 回滚
    H --> C: err "caller-not-lead-in-any-team"
  end

  loop 每个 caller-lead team (firstTeam 优先)
    H -> TR: swapLead(teamId, callerSid, newSid, {newDisplayName})
    note right of TR
      swap lead role 从 caller 转给 newSid
      teammate 与 newSid 共享 active team
      可继续 send_message 沟通
    end note

    alt swap 失败
      alt firstTeam (lead 角色起源)
        H -> SM: closeSession(newSid) firstTeam fatal abort
        H --> C: err "first-team-swap-failed"
      else 非 firstTeam (软失败)
        H -> H: adopted.failed.push({sid, reason})\n非 firstTeam 软失败继续 loop
      end
    end

    H -> DB: lifecycle precheck swap 后 team teammate\n(closed teammate fail-fast filter)
    H -> H: adopted.preserved.push(swappedTeamId)
  end
else adopt_teammates == false (default 纯 baton)
  H -> H: skip phase 1.5,走 phase 1+2 cleanup\n(原 teammate 与 newSid 无 shared team,send_message 撞 no-shared-team)
end

== Phase 1.6: task 三态分流 (v024 plan task-team-id-restore-20260525) ==

alt archive_caller == false
  H -> H: skip task reassign\n(caller 仍 active 继续 own 自己 task)
  H -> H: taskReassignment = {status:'skipped', reason:'archive-caller-false', policy}
else team_task_policy == 'clear-team' (default)
  H -> Tk: reassignTaskOwner(callerSid, newSid, {policy:'clear-team'})
  Tk -> DB: UPDATE tasks SET owner_session_id=newSid, team_id=NULL\n  WHERE owner_session_id=callerSid
  note right of Tk
    过继 ownership 同时清 team_id 变 personal task
    newSid 拿到的 task 都可写,适用面最广
  end note
  Tk --> H: rowCount
else team_task_policy == 'preserve-team' (caller 自负责任)
  H -> Tk: reassignTaskOwner(callerSid, newSid, {policy:'preserve-team'})
  Tk -> DB: UPDATE tasks SET owner_session_id=newSid (不动 team_id)
  H -> Tk: findCallerOwnedTeamIds(callerSid)
  Tk -> DB: SELECT DISTINCT team_id WHERE owner=caller AND team_id NOT NULL
  H -> H: 比对 adoptedTeamIds ∪ spawnData.teamId 差集\n→ unadoptedTeamIds (policyWarning='preserve-team-unadopted-teams')
else team_task_policy == 'skip' (清理场景)
  H -> Tk: applyHandOffSkipPolicy(callerSid, newSid)
  Tk -> DB: 单 transaction 4 步原子:\n  1. SELECT caller team task ids snapshot\n  2. DELETE chunked (CHUNK=500)\n  3. blocks/blocked_by 引用 cleanup\n  4. UPDATE owner SET newSid WHERE team_id IS NULL
  Tk --> H: { deletedTeamTaskIds, reassignedPersonalCount }
end

H -> H: 失败兜底: reassign throw 仅 warn 不阻塞\nok return.taskReassignment 字段透传结果

== Phase 2: runBatonCleanup (与 archive_plan 共享 helper) ==

H -> BC: runBatonCleanup({callerSid, toolName: 'hand_off_session'},\n  {shutdownTeammates: (sid, exclude) => helper(sid, {excludeSessionIds: exclude → newSid})})
note right of BC
  REVIEW_36 R2 HIGH-A: shutdownTeammates seam
  加 excludeSessionIds 参数显式排除新 spawn 的 newSid
  防 team_name=x baton 路径下新 session 被 spawn 加为 teammate
  然后被 helper 一并 close
end note

alt adopt_teammates == true
  BC -> BC: phase 1 skip (skipped='adopt-keep-implicit')
else
  BC -> SM: phase 1: shutdownTeammatesOnBaton(callerSid, {exclude: {newSid}})\n  → close 同 team 全部 active+dormant teammate
end

alt archive_caller == false
  BC -> BC: phase 2 skip (skipped='archive-caller-false')
else
  BC -> SM: phase 2: archiveSourceSessionWithEmit(callerSid)\n  → callerRow.archived_at = ISO + eventBus emit
end

BC --> H: { teammatesShutdown, archived }

== Handler 收口 ok return ==

H --> C: ok({\n  mode: 'plan' | 'generic',\n  planId, planFilePath, worktreePath, initialPrompt, phaseLabel,\n  sessionId, cwd, teamId, teamName, spawnPromptMessageId,\n  archived, teammatesShutdown,\n  adopted?: {preserved, failed, teamsTotal, teamsAdopted, firstTeamId},\n  taskReassignment: {status, count, policy, policyWarning?, unadoptedTeamIds?}\n})

@enduml
